import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { CustomerService } from '../customer.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-profile', templateUrl: './profile.component.html', styleUrls: ['./profile.component.css'] }) export class ProfileComponent { users:any constructor(private customerService:CustomerService) { } ngOnInit() { this.customerService.ViewUserProfile() .subscribe(response => { this.users = response; console.log(response); }); } }
